# Prefer automatic setup: commit real op:// paths in **intake/local.env.op.defaults**
# (tracked) — first checkpoint run copies to gitignored **intake/local.env.op**.
# Or copy this file manually:
#   cp intake/local.env.op.example intake/local.env.op
#
# Docs: docs/intake-local-prereqs.md § Local 1Password env (auto op run)
#
# After local.env.op exists, these scripts re-exec under `op run` automatically:
#   intake/scripts/pipeline-preflight.sh
#   intake/scripts/iteration-checkpoints.sh
# (Unless INTAKE_OP_AUTO_DISABLE=1.)
#
# Reference syntax: https://developer.1password.com/docs/cli/secret-reference-syntax/

# Linear: prefer OAuth access token (e.g. Morgan OAuth developer_token), not lin_api_* keys
LINEAR_API_KEY=op://Automation/Linear Morgan OAuth/developer_token

# Discord bridge (local): OpenClaw intake bot token
DISCORD_BRIDGE_TOKEN=op://Automation/OpenClaw Discord Tokens/DISCORD_TOKEN_INTAKE

# Optional: bridge bases when not using in-cluster DNS (no trailing slash)
# DISCORD_BRIDGE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3200
# LINEAR_BRIDGE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3100
